data.description: Beautiful five bedroom, three full and one half bath home with sunroom extension located in sought-after Dunleigh neighborhood.  Enjoy an open floor plan drenched in bright sunlight with a view of the neighborhood park across the street.  Large eat in kitchen with cherry cabinets, vaulted ceiling, recessed lighting, and open view to the dining and living room area.  Sunroom extension from the living room and doors leading out to a tiered deck with twin gazebos and built-in table make this a serene setting to relax in. Cherry hardwood floors on main level. Family room with brick wood burning fireplace. Half bath is located on this level. Fifth bedroom or office with second washer and dryer hookup, if needed, with walk out to lower deck. Top floor with two level primary bedroom includes a sitting area and three closets (two with closet organizers).  Primary bath with dual sinks and beautifully tiled shower.  Three additional bedrooms and another full bath are located on this level.  If this is not enough room to stretch out in, proceed to the lower levels.  Another entertainment area with sauna, rec room, and full bath.  Finally, a large storage area with shelves, possible wood working shop, finishes the house on the lowest level.  Two car garage.  Fenced, landscaped backyard with path and lights.  Roof replaced including both gazebos September 2021, Pella front windows July 2021, Pella back windows May 2014, Courier HVAC and indoor unit December 2018, whole house surge protector November 2016. Commuter’s dream with bus stop at the front of neighborhood and access to the VRE.  Walk to Lake Braddock Secondary School, Kings Park Library, and shopping and restaurants at King Park Shopping Center.
